title: Group Therapy: The Emergency Group Therapy
description: "A" emailed us and needed us to do Group Therapy ASAP.   Her sister is going to Puerto Rico by herself and A found out she's going to meet up with a random guy she met online.  She's concerned for her sister's safety so she' wondering if she should tell her parents or what she should do?
